<headline>Special Weather Statement issued January 03 at 7:54AM EST  by NWS Cleveland</headline>
<description>...PATCHY FREEZING DRIZZLE THIS MORNING...
Drizzle will continue this morning, with patches of freezing
drizzle as well. This could lead to a light glaze of ice on
untreated surfaces. Any freezing drizzle will end by 10 AM as
surface temperatures rise above freezing.
Slow down and allow extra time to reach your destination this
morning. Roads, bridges, and overpasses that just look wet may be
icy.</description>
